{
  "verses": [
    {
      "verse_num": 1,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "When Israel came out of Egypt, Jacob's descendants from a people of foreign language,"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 2,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "Judah became God's sanctuary, Israel his dominion."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 3,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "The sea looked and fled, the Jordan turned back;"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 4,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "the mountains leaped like rams, the hills like lambs."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 5,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "Why was it, sea, that you fled? Why, Jordan, did you turn back?"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 6,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "Why, mountains, did you leap like rams, you hills, like lambs?"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 7,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "Tremble, earth, at the presence of the Lord, at the presence of the God of Jacob,"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 8,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "who turned the rock into a pool of water, the hard rock into springs of water."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    }
  ]
}